{"tid":2261074,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國第一夫人梅拉尼婭親自挽救侵侵「賓州」！","createTime":"2020-10-28T05:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T05:16:33.000Z","uid":219635,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a75b2efbecaf54ec2d5e3a30d4b3a8886494be","tid":2261074,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"梅拉尼婭出席的活動將由前白宮高級顧問康韋（Kellyanne Conway）主持。康韋向霍士新聞（Fox News）透露，梅拉尼婭將提到自己如何幫助賓夕法尼亞州，並指出如果特朗普成功連任，美國人將再享受四年自由、繁榮、安全和充滿機遇的生活。<br />\n<br />\n康韋提到，四年前特朗普參選時，梅拉尼婭單獨前往賓夕法尼亞州拉票是勝出選舉的關鍵。賓夕法尼亞州也是四年前梅拉尼婭於共和黨全國代表大會後首個前往的州份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c958f7ebf3ccb84e853e9c1194dac76be0d81689","tid":2261074,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faaf4a21d4cd7caedc674b647af6f014a4a378f","tid":2261074,"uid":219635,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"侵侵賓州比拜登軟弱，今次輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d6537902ff46fdbdbeaa007d70f665e47fb588","tid":2261074,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824db22c27a3802a68da9bfbfefe73f80c9ec09d","tid":2261074,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:15:24.000Z","ms